full_text:
For the record I could care less that people know Hayden paid me back. I was fully planning on saying it on the live stream but he caught me off guard by texting me in the middle of it and asking me not to mention it.  You can actually see my eyes read the text in real time during the stream. I didn’t know why he cared but figured I’d better find out before mentioning it live.   After the spaces was over I asked him why he didn’t want me to say it and his answer was because he still needed time to figure out how to make this right for as many people as he could without everybody screaming at him where is my money..  Ok fine whatever.  It didn’t really change the story for me. I knew people could see my wallet anyway. 

Also if the situation was reversed I would have 100% paid him back.  He fully led me to believe he was in lock step with Milei and I think he thought he was.  I did a ton of research on Milei and was impressed with him.  I would have never been involved without Hayden vouching for him.  And If I vouch for a guy and hyped up a cool project that turned out to be a fraud I’d pay them back too regardless of whose fault it was.  Also Hayden made it clear he was paying me from his personal money.  I got no idea if that’s true or not.  I was just happy to get it back and so would have every other person in my shoes.  If you get robbed and somebody is like I can get your shit back you take it.  

Ps - I included the texts from the live stream and right after as well as him saying it was his personal money
name: Dave Portnoy
